        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2895205099" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer293239575259113672">Wonderful book and a very timely read given the references to &quot;Orwellian&quot; terms such as doublethink, 2 minutes hate, thought police etc bandied about in these strange days in which we live. I was interested to learn about his careers as a police officer and working for the BBC, both of which inspired 1984. And, of course, this is by the late, great Christopher Hitchens who was a genius, so it was beautifully written.</span>
  <span id="freeText293239575259113672" style="display:none">Wonderful book and a very timely read given the references to "Orwellian" terms such as doublethink, 2 minutes hate, thought police etc bandied about in these strange days in which we live. I was interested to learn about his careers as a police officer and working for the BBC, both of which inspired 1984. And, of course, this is by the late, great Christopher Hitchens who was a genius, so it was beautifully written.</span>
