          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback " href="/book/show/53243170-why-orwell-matters">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/47087997-piers-haslam?shelf=essays">essays</a>, 
