<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/9648.Keep_the_Aspidistra_Flying"><img alt="Keep the Aspidistra Flying" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1331244097l/9648._SX98_.jpg" />
